title: #80: Legalize Weirdness with Mistress Justine Cross
description: Thank you for tuning into another fun episode of Tin Foil Hat.  This episode the guys welcome Dominatrix Justine Cross to discuss the controversy surrounding the Sex Trafficking Bill, FOSTA or H.R.1865. Explore whether this bill actually does anything to help stop sex trafficking or will it just lead to more internet censorship?  All of this and more on this episode of Tin Foil Hat!
